Version: 0.5.7
Summary: √áe≈üitli graf k√ºt√ºphaneleri i√ßin sƒ±ralƒ±-zigzag yerle≈üimleri saƒülayan bir Python paketi.
Home-page: https://github.com/WhiteSymmetry/kececilayout
